			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>One of the regular posters to these forums has a magelo link.  On that link, you can see his HP, and the breakdown between std hp, direct adds and indrect (via stamina)- the numbers were like 2300 base 1700 direct and 500 indirect.  Mind you he has some awsome gear.  The point that I am trying to make is that you will be sacrificing about 300 hp if you dont re-do your char - not a big deal in the scheme of things.  Everyone will have a different opinion about which stats are better (I remember when AGI was king, then DEX then CHR) but in the end how you play will affect your successes much more that 25 pts in one stat.
<br />

