				<td colspan="2"><span>Fishing grubs are in my ammo slot until I get VoS.  Basically, when you die, and can't get a rez right away, loot all your stuff from your corpse, except the fish grubs. THat way you have all your gear to fight some more and don't &quot;dry loot&quot; your corpse. When you get a rez, simply loot your grubs and go on from there.  
